      "message": "[🔴 Critical] Line 2081: updateMessageBodyOverwrite() only propagates an edition overwrite to the parent when latestEditionId matches, but it does not clear the parent\u0027s existing bodyOverwrite when bodyOverwrite is empty. Clearing the latest edition overwrite can therefore leave stale translated/current text visible on the parent. Erase the parent overwrite when the current edition is cleared.\n```suggestion\nif (parentIt-\u003esecond-\u003elatestEditionId \u003d\u003d messageId) {\n    if (bodyOverwrite.empty())\n        parentIt-\u003esecond-\u003epluginData.erase(\"bodyOverwrite\");\n    else\n        parentIt-\u003esecond-\u003epluginData[\"bodyOverwrite\"] \u003d bodyOverwrite;\n}\n```",
